com.bigdata.rdf.sparql.ast.optimizers

Class ASTALPServiceOptimizer

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.bigdata.rdf.sparql.ast.optimizers.AbstractJoinGroupOptimizer
      • com.bigdata.rdf.sparql.ast.optimizers.ASTALPServiceOptimizer
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IASTOptimizer

    public class ASTALPServiceOptimizer
extends AbstractJoinGroupOptimizer
implements IASTOptimizer
    This ALP SERVICE IASTOptimizer provides a rewrite of a SERVICE expression that makes it possible to specify limits (minimum, maximum path length), directionality of traversal, etc.

    A sample query is: 

     #e.g. "Go three hops out in either direction from vertex  where the edge is of type  and the edge has =someVal."
 
 SELECT * WHERE {
 SERVICE bd:alp { " +
  ?edge ?to . " +
 hint:Prior hint:alp.pathExpr true .
 ?edge rdf:type  .
 ?edge  "someVal" .
 hint:Group hint:alp.lowerBound 1 .
 hint:Group hint:alp.upperBound 3 .
 hint:Group hint:alp.bidirectional true .
 }
 }
    Author:
    bryan
